com.facebook.buck.sandbox

Class SandboxProperties.Builder

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.facebook.buck.sandbox.SandboxProperties.Builder
  • Enclosing class:
    SandboxProperties

    @NotThreadSafe
public static final class SandboxProperties.Builder
extends Object
    Builds instances of type SandboxProperties. Initialize attributes and then invoke the build() method to create an immutable instance.

    Builder is not thread-safe and generally should not be stored in a field or collection, but instead used immediately to create instances.

        public final SandboxProperties.Builder from(SandboxProperties instance)
        Fill a builder with attribute values from the provided SandboxProperties instance. Regular attribute values will be replaced with those from the given instance. Absent optional values will not replace present values. Collection elements and entries will be added, not replaced.
